{"lemma":"سُوقَة","slug":"سُوقَة","root":"س.#.ق","root_slug":"س-_-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/س-_-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n21293"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%8F%D9%88%D9%82%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n21293","headword_ar":"سُوقَةٌ","root":"swq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A subject,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"subjects,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a king; (K, TA;) so called because driven by him; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malikN","text_ar":"مَلِكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, Mgh, Msb;) whether practising traffic or not: (Mgh:) not meaning of the people of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asowaAq","text_ar":"اَسْوَاق"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or markets], as the vulgar think; (Msb;) for such are called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suwqiy~uwna","text_ar":"سُوقِيُّونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", sing."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suwqiY~N","text_ar":"سُوقِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Ham p. 534:) it is used alike as sing. and pl. (S, Mgh, Msb, K) and dual (Mgh, Msb) and masc. and fem.: (S, K:) but sometimes it has"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suwaqN","text_ar":"سُوَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"for its pl. (S, K.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suwqapu AlT~urovuwvi","text_ar":"سُوقَةُ الطُّرْثُوثِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the CK, erroneously,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~urovuwvi","text_ar":"التُّرْثُوثِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The part of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plant called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Trvwv","text_ar":"طرثوث"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is below the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nikoEap","text_ar":"نِكْعَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nakaEap","text_ar":"نَكَعَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nukaEap","text_ar":"نُكَعَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"head from the top to the extent of a finger,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flower at the head thereof"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (O, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sweet and pleasant:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so says Ibn-' Abbád: (O:) AHn says [of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Trvwv","text_ar":"طرثوث"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it is like the penis of the ass, and there is no part of it more pleasant, nor sweeter, than its"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"swqp","text_ar":"سوقة"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is in some instances long; and in some, short."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suwqN","text_ar":"سُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", last sentence."}],"source_refs":["Mgh","S","Msb","K","O"]}]}}